## Schedule 4

All that parcel of land containing 1 rood and 8 perches, more or less, being that part of Block XXXVII, Town of Patea, bounded towards the north-east by public reserve, 200 links; towards the south-east by other part of the said Block XXXVII, 150 links; towards the south-west by Egmont Street, 200 links; and towards the north-west by Victoria Street, 150 links; and being part of the land comprised in certificate of title, Register-book, Volume 56, folio 166, Taranaki Registry.

